txt.en: 'Meow! Oh, you are up to Book IX. This was where you learned that the dottering old fool Sara Oakheart was really Amarthiel in disguise. Very exciting!\n\nBut none of that for you! You'll be flagged as having completed Book IX if you speak to me again.
'Completion of Book IX coming up!\n\nOh, and if I were you, I would hold on to something... you are in for a bit of a bumpy ride....'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book IX of the Epic quest series.
